---
/* small grid of feature cards used in the page */
---
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Better, together.</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Analytics To Help Your Business Grow Stronger Everyday.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold"><i class="fa-solid custom-size-icon fa-chart-bar"></i> &nbsp; Dashboarding</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Latest Visualization Softwares allow for actionable information to improve business performance outcomes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold"><i class="fa-solid custom-size-icon fa-database"></i> &nbsp; Data Warehousing</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Put your Data in a cloud hosted and managed PostgreSQL instance to keep track of many sources with export capabilities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold"><i class="fa-solid custom-size-icon fa-robot"></i> &nbsp; LLM Powered Insights</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Chat with your data with latest OpenAI models and understand the mathematical and statistical inferences that allow for improved business decisions. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg text-center">
        <div class="mb-3 font-semibold"><i class="fa-solid custom-size-icon fa-wand-sparkles"></i> &nbsp; Automate Workflows</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Automate your workflows from message bots to data entry to scheduling.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="pricing"></div>
</section>
